eutros.multiblocktweaker.crafttweaker.construction

类 MultiblockBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • eutros.multiblocktweaker.crafttweaker.construction.MultiblockBuilder

  • public class MultiblockBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    The Builder, or Multiblock Builder, is used to define a custom CustomMultiblock.

    To get started, call start(String, int).

    ZenClass:
    mods.gregtech.multiblock.Builder

    • 方法详细资料

      • start

        public static MultiblockBuilder start(@NotNull
                                      @NotNull java.lang.String location,
                                      int metaId)
        Create a multiblock builder from a resource location.
        参数:
        location - The resource location of the multiblock. Used for getting the recipe map again. If no namespace is defined, it defaults to this mod's mod id.
        metaId - (optional) The metadata the resulting multiblock will be registered as. A non-used ID is automatically registered if metaId is empty.
        返回:
        A multiblock builder instance, that should be used to set the properties of the multiblock.

      • start

        Create a multiblock builder from a resource location.

        location - The resource location of the multiblock. Used for getting the recipe map again. If no namespace is defined, it defaults to this mod's mod id.
        返回:
        A multiblock builder instance, that should be used to set the properties of the multiblock.

      • withBaseTexture

        public MultiblockBuilder withBaseTexture(@NotNull
                                         @NotNull IICubeRenderer texture)
        Set the texture for the multiblock. This will be used for the controller, and all the inputs/outputs when the structure forms.

        If this is not defined, build() will fail.

        参数:
        texture - The texture to use.
        返回:
        This builder, for convenience.

      • addDesign

        public MultiblockBuilder addDesign(@NotNull
                                   IMultiblockShapeInfo... designs)
        Add a design to be shown in JEI or structure previews. Can be called multiple times.

        If none are defined, the multiblock will use the auto way.

        参数:
        designs - The designs to add and show in JEI.
        返回:
        This builder, for convenience.

      • build

        @Nullable
public CustomMultiblock build()
        Construct the CustomMultiblock using the defined features.

        Will fail if withPattern(IPatternBuilderFunction) or withRecipeMap(RecipeMap) wasn't called, or if withBaseTexture(IICubeRenderer) wasn't called.

        返回:
        The built CustomMultiblock.

      • buildAndRegister

        @Nullable
public CustomMultiblock buildAndRegister()
        Convenience method, equivalent to build().register()

        返回:
        The built CustomMultiblock.
        另请参阅:
        build(), CustomMultiblock.register()
